154
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,480
You've to cover your tracks.

155
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:03,560
There's a pen repair shop in Wenmiao Street.

156
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:04,260
Remember,

157
00:13:04,730 --> 00:13:06,450
you replaced it two days ago.

158
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,850
It cost 3.6 yuan.

159
00:13:10,110 --> 00:13:11,360
So you suspect me?

160
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,080
Why?

161
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,100
Shouldn't we?

162
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,140
Kai.

163
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:56,790
