164
00:13:58,470 --> 00:13:59,800
How did you know it's me?

165
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:04,320
Look at your shaky hands. Practice more.

166
00:14:07,110 --> 00:14:08,630
I never have guests.

167
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:10,390
It's my first time.

168
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,160
I thought I could scare you.

169
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:14,120
