170
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:18,470
Walther PPK?

171
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:20,350
Nice one.

172
00:14:22,110 --> 00:14:23,070
I can take you

173
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:26,070
to the suburbs to hunt rabbits.

174
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:28,430
The gun's bullets are hard to find.

175
00:14:28,430 --> 00:14:29,470
Only four left.

176
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:31,270
Forget it.

177
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:32,860
I gave him the gun.

178
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:35,750
Our job makes many enemies.

179
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:37,800
He's always home alone.

180
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:39,630
It's good to be careful.

181
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,120
I bought some food,

182
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,230
