183
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,570
I came early.

184
00:14:52,230 --> 00:14:52,950
Come on.

185
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:27,820
You can even cook?

186
00:15:29,010 --> 00:15:30,210
Unlike you,

187
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:32,270
I have

188
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,870
a mouth to feed.

189
00:15:35,430 --> 00:15:36,560
I've to make it work.

190
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:39,370
Be honest.

191
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:41,390
Did I scare you just now?

192
00:15:44,350 --> 00:15:45,140
No.

193
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:46,820
It's a formality.

194
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:48,000
I know the rules.

195
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,270
If it's a formality,

196
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:53,580
