197
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:03,720
Thank you.

198
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:06,010
I thought you don't drink.

199
00:16:06,010 --> 00:16:07,210
I don't drink outside.

200
00:16:07,210 --> 00:16:08,470
Aren't we at your home?

201
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:11,030
You're forward.

202
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:14,180
Good wine.

203
00:16:18,650 --> 00:16:19,910
Pan Yue said I'm scary.

204
00:16:22,950 --> 00:16:24,080
Are you afraid of me?

205
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,350
I'm just a pawn in your hands,

206
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:29,550
under your control.

207
00:16:29,810 --> 00:16:31,010
What's there to fear?

208
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:34,040
You're not a pawn.

209
00:16:35,860 --> 00:16:37,230
You should be a knife.

210
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:39,670
Wait.

211
00:16:40,430 --> 00:16:41,720
Isn’t that Xiaojiang?

212
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
I can’t be a knife.

213
00:16:46,380 --> 00:16:47,410
You're acting

214
00:16:47,590 --> 00:16:49,030
like I wronged you.

215
00:16:51,290 --> 00:16:52,090
No.

216
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:53,910
What did I do?

217
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:54,920
No, no, no.

218
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:56,550
No. I'm sorry.

219
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:59,210
I should've invited you home for dinner sooner.

220
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:00,470
A meal's

221
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,990
no big deal.

222
00:17:02,890 --> 00:17:05,150
You must've thought you would

223
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,420
work less and earn more

224
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:09,030
as a special agent.

225
00:17:10,020 --> 00:17:11,260
But in fact,

226
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,710
it's daily bloodshed.

227
00:17:15,010 --> 00:17:16,670
You were even nearly wronged.

228
00:17:17,890 --> 00:17:19,349
If I were you, I'd think...

229
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:21,020
it's not worth it.

230
00:17:39,490 --> 00:17:42,010
How will you deal with Tian Xiaojiang?

231
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:45,330
In the Secret Service,

232
00:17:46,710 --> 00:17:48,350
don't ask what you shouldn't ask.

233
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:49,840
Don't see what you shouldn't see.

234
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:51,470
-Yes.
-Don't say what you shouldn't say.

235
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:52,660
Yes.

236
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:58,830
Don't just stand there.

237
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:00,510
Mix the noodles.

238
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,330
Look at me.

239
00:18:14,430 --> 00:18:15,560
Pour some wine, Kai.

240
00:18:19,870 --> 00:18:21,330
We risk our lives everyday

241
00:18:21,630 --> 00:18:24,190
just to have a meal on the table.

242
00:18:25,420 --> 00:18:26,830
Zhuowen, wait a bit longer.

243
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,150
After I find your brother,

244
00:18:28,150 --> 00:18:29,410
you'll be with family.

245
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:30,660
Come on.

246
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:31,340
Come on.

247
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,280
Thank you, Ms. Guan.

248
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:40,270
I'll dig in then.

249
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:47,740
Here, Kai.

250
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:57,930
It's for me.

251
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:58,800
Eat up.

252
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:01,450
Zhuowen, eat up.

253
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:03,160
Her calls take forever.

254
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:10,470
Hello?

255
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:11,540
Ms. Guan.

256
00:19:11,950 --> 00:19:13,740
You asked us to tail Mr. Fan.

257
00:19:14,150 --> 00:19:15,150
