258
00:19:15,150 --> 00:19:16,470
with guards everywhere.

259
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,600
It's impenetrable.

260
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:21,070
Mr. Fan's wife runs the casino

261
00:19:21,090 --> 00:19:22,970
in Far Eastern Department Store.

262
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:25,010
Go there when you're free.

263
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:25,810
Here.

264
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,710
-Thank you.
-Do I have to teach you everything?

265
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:28,750
Dating anyone?

266
00:19:28,990 --> 00:19:30,230
Who'd like me?

267
00:19:31,220 --> 00:19:33,080
The girl with the pockmarked face at the counter.

268
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,810
Your sister won't let you date?

269
00:19:35,230 --> 00:19:36,150
No.

270
00:19:36,150 --> 00:19:37,030
Talk to her.

271
00:19:38,470 --> 00:19:40,550
Girls get scared when they know

272
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:41,960
she's my sister.

273
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:43,610
Is she that scary?

274
00:19:44,350 --> 00:19:46,190
Don't you work at the Secret Service?

275
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:47,480
You'll find out.

276
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,430
Badmouthing me?

277
00:19:50,770 --> 00:19:53,210
Kai asked me about work.

278
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:55,910
Zhuowen.

279
00:19:57,250 --> 00:19:58,160
Don't be a cop.

280
00:19:58,650 --> 00:19:59,840
It's too dangerous.

281
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:03,470
Everyone's seeking peace

282
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,670
in this chaotic times,

283
00:20:07,650 --> 00:20:09,490
so it's a lucrative job.

284
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:12,670
You're being used by the Japanese

285
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:14,140
and scolded by your people.

286
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,140
It's not worth it.

287
00:20:15,930 --> 00:20:17,470
You can't live for money.

288
00:20:19,140 --> 00:20:20,600
What are you trying to say?

289
00:20:24,210 --> 00:20:25,240
You students

290
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,630
are brainwashed by

291
00:20:27,630 --> 00:20:28,510
Chongqing

292
00:20:28,860 --> 00:20:30,190
and Yan'an broadcasts.

293
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:33,220
Be it the Qing dynasty

294
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:34,480
or the Republic of China,

295
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:36,540
